extendedInfo.description: Mobile Banking from Pinnacle Bank allows you to easily and quickly review account activity, transfer funds, pay bills and check your account balances from your mobile phone.Mobile Banking is a FREE* service from PInnacle Bank that allows you to access your accounts anytime, from anywhere, using your Android device.Features:-Check account balances-Pay bills** and transfer funds-View account alerts-Locate nearby branches and ATM'sSecurity:-Mobile Banking from Pinnacle Bank provides the same level of security as Online Banking-Your personal information is protected by multiple layers of the latest in encryption and security technology.- No sensitive data is stored on your mobile phone.To access Mobile Banking, you must be an Online Banking user.  Visit www.pinnaclebank.com to enroll in Online Banking or contact your personal banker.Member FDIC*There is no fee from Pinnacle Bank.  Connectivity and usage rates may apply.  Contact your wireless service provider for more details.  **User must be enrolled in BIll Pay to pay bills using Mobile Banking.  New payees must be setup in Online BankingAndroid is a Trademark of Google Inc.
